    "en": {
      "title": "Gota's Mirihana residence heavily guarded",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Measures have been taken to strengthen the security of former President Gotabhaya Rajapaksa's private residence in Mirihan.",
        "It is notable that more security personnel have been deployed in that house than the number previously deployed and commando force officers have been deployed to strengthen the security.",
        "Former President Gotabhaya Rajapaksa had announced earlier that he would return to Sri Lanka today (24), but it was later read that his arrival will be delayed by two weeks."
      ],
